{"tid":2159423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔計外國出世果班，有邊個香港出世藝人英文勁過宣萱？","createTime":"2020-08-16T10:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T21:03:22.000Z","uid":118346,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f174bd7b594db4c372d1317011e99510712752b3","tid":2159423,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oVjAv9_XT0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoVjAv9_XT0c&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=2e5df3c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oVjAv9_XT0c</a><br />\n好好聽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宣萱英文名「Jessica」是爸爸替她取的，「Hester」是媽媽給她另外取的一個名字，英文全名為：Jessica Hester Hsuan。宣萱兒時先後就讀瑪利諾修院學校小學部和香港培道中學，13歲的時候前往英國留學，就讀英國南部女子寄宿學校羅丁中學（Roedean School）。1992年畢業於倫敦大學帝國理工學院（Imperial College London, University of London）並獲得材料工程學學士學位。"},{"pid":"056803c373e66ecff187631d75a1e90d4193aa9e","tid":2159423,"uid":124277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61746998a609b963244feb00c42497250d380843","tid":2159423,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"Dodo"},{"pid":"cc22336795b3c12b45a70f15c9fa52beee6ce4f2","tid":2159423,"uid":118346,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"056803c373e66ecff187631d75a1e90d4193aa9e","tid":2159423,"uid":124277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"He is also one of my 飛佛"},{"pid":"ab2c04667d518305186c207b826d27687af367cc","tid":2159423,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61746998a609b963244feb00c42497250d380843","tid":2159423,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2